Whether you're looking for a practical gift for a co-worker, a thoughtful gift for a friend, our leather notebook is sure to please!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really wasn’t expecting much from this low-priced journal but I wanted something with a gazillion pages in it & this one had 320. The first thing that struck me (happily I might add) was the quality of the paper! At 100gsm it’s smooth but not shiny with the slightest touch of tooth I find so satisfying for drawing upon. I use my journal on a daily basis and I often sketch on the pages. The paper is off-white/ cream/ ivory which I prefer to stark bright white. There are 6 table of content pages in the front followed by unnumbered pages that say “Date:” in the upper right or left hand corners. It would be easy enough to number the pages as you go along if that’s what you want. The journal is A5 size (approximately 5.5”x8.25”) which is a perfect size for a daily journal IMO.There are two bookmarks, an elastic band, pen loop & back pocket. The only “con” is it’s on the heavy side, but I don’t use my daily as an EDC so even that’s not really a problem for me.I am super happy with this purchase & plan to grab another one if they aren’t sold out already!!
